{"tid":902598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙 11 後現退款潮！淘寶系統崩壞hang機？","createTime":"2018-11-15T02:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T09:50:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4acea0ecceda70ac741a2f0998bce77ad2a76b15","tid":902598,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2205000/2208343/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2205000%2F2208343%2F1_1024.jpg&h=a8499ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前雙 11 網購節引來民瘋狂購物，在短短 2 分鐘，成交額已經達 100 億元人民幣，最終全日交易總額高達 2135 億元人民幣。從另一個角度看，後續問題也不少，很多人因商品質量、衣服尺寸不合等原因，出現了退款潮，令淘寶退款頁面崩潰。在百度熱搜榜中，「淘寶退款崩了」排名更一度居首！<br />\n<br />\n據內地媒體報道，由於天貓雙十一規則限制，當天購買的東西不能退款，到了翌日零時，後悔衝動消費的人都馬上忙著退款。不過當中不少人發現，搶貨的時候沒有事，退款的時候卻當機了，介面只出現「系統繁忙，稍後重試」。網民紛紛在微信抱怨，「淘寶退款崩了」這關鍵詞隨即登上百度熱搜，更一度成為第一位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2205000/2208343/20181112173249292_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2205000%2F2208343%2F20181112173249292_600.jpg&h=ada1cf3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了質量欠佳、衝動消費等問題，其實愈來愈多人發現，所謂雙 11 活動，不一定便宜很多，部份商品只是玩數字遊戲，跟平時的售價沒有太大分別，偶然甚至會出現雙 11 更貴的情況。有年輕人直指： 「老實說，我甚至都覺得這麼多給你設置這麼多數學題，就是為了隱藏其實根本沒優惠多少的事實。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2205000/2208343/20181112173200914_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2205000%2F2208343%2F20181112173200914_600.jpg&h=f5e4d9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2208343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2208343&d=kik4d0YPBIva1UE5XH0I60jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=e243acba\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2208343</a>"},{"pid":"29478ea6967f710c6789c6d2c9f85730d6defe66","tid":902598,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:56:38.000Z","msg":"同支那股票一樣<br />\n只准買不准沽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad08643602e36cbe190782fe2b96edd242894c87","tid":902598,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:57:36.000Z","msg":"刷業績刷到撞車姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ee203ef2452722685f7d7552f5d515342bdfee","tid":902598,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:58:31.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486a3b1349e63c4e715aac2baca2a7c36a5fe8c2","tid":902598,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"預咗啦, 年年都退貨, 佢地都有心理準備."},{"pid":"3ef13966cd993a63d317a208bf2153e44d46bb81","tid":902598,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}